titles.title: To designate a portion of United States Route 20A, located in Orchard Park, New York, as the "Timothy J. Russert Highway".

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Highways and Transit.

bill.summary:
6/19/2008--Introduced.
Designates the portion of U.S. Route 20A located in Orchard Park, New York, between Abbot Road and California Road, as the "Timothy J. Russert Highway."
